he eye. Once the cataract is cleared then an Intraocular lens is introduced in the eye in a folded manner through the original opening. This lens then unfolds in the eye.\r\nAs the wound is small, it heals fast. The patient can get back to his routine the next day itself. However, as an added precaution, it is advisable to avoid hectic activities and outdoor jobs for the first week.\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Treatments', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '88-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-08-18 12:57:26', '2017-08-18 12:57:26', '', 88, 'http://localhost/salim/88-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
